                <div class="card">
                    <div class="content-image zoom">
                                                                                <a href="#">
                                                            <img decoding="async" class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="/assets-f/img/5e5999b47ece2b.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="640">
                                                        </a>
                                                                        </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                                                    <div class="body">
                                <h3 class="h6">Our services</h3>
<p>As a full services construction company, our services begin before you break ground, through your project and beyond. With multiple delivery methods and specialty services (including project planning, bond services and historic preservation) our team is dedicated to your success.</p>
                            </div>
                        
                                                    <div class="content-cta">
                                <a href="#" target="" class="btn btn-outline-primary-green">Learn more</a>
                            </div>
                                            </div>
                </div>
            </div>
